Introduction

Youngjun is in charge of keyboard in the group NND. Youngjun, who has been closely involved with music since childhood due to the influence of his mother, a guitar instructor, built a solid foundation with piano and drums and passed the audition to become a band trainee while preparing for the piano entrance exam to major in applied music.

From then on, he felt himself expanding beyond the piano in terms of speed, quality, and quantity of music, and his views on music changed. Youngjun, who believes that the value of music is only realized when the public chooses and sings it, has reflected this in his [Wonder, I] album work to elicit a stable sympathy from listeners.

Youngjun played keyboard for former member TraxX‘s Jungmo‘s song ‘Marionette‘ and also appeared in the music video.
He was also featured as a keyboardist on Brown Eyed Girls‘ JeA‘s cover of ‘Love Wins All’ (original by IU).

On February 26, 2025 Way Better announced Youngjun now going by YYJ as a new artist making fans believe that NND has silently disbanded.
